modName: Smexy female Altmer - lvl 1 high elf

descriptionHtml:
I haven\'t used any mods on her except No More Blocky Faces...
http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/downloads/file.php?id=30

Even without that, she\'ll look pretty much as advertised in the pics.

Her name is Wundercunt. I know it\'s stupid and inappropriate, but when I created her I hadn\'t planned on sharing her with anybody soooo.... if it offends you, just open the console and type \"showracemenu\" to change her name.

Update: I added the file. Forgive my retardedness >_<

Edit: I added a 3rd pic using Xenius\' Detailed Lips and Detailed Faces v2... I highly recommend them:
